r seamless theme integration"},"217":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-43","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#features","content":"**Accessibility ready**: Built-in support for screen readers and keyboard navigation"},"218":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-44","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#features","content":"**TypeScript support**: Fully typed with comprehensive prop interfaces"},"219":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-45","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#features","content":"**Bento integration**: Extends Bento Icon with additional UXCore-specific features"},"220":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-46","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#props","content":"The `Icon` component accepts the following props:"},"221":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-47","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#prop-inheritance","content":"The component extends `BentoIconProps` and passes through all standard HTML attributes and accessibility props to the underlying Bento Icon component. This includes:"},"222":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-48","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#prop-inheritance","content":"**Accessibility**: `aria-label`, `aria-describedby`, `role`, `title`"},"223":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-49","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#prop-inheritance","content":"**Events**: `onClick`, `onMouseOver`, `onFocus`, etc."},"224":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-50","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#prop-inheritance","content":"**Styling**: `className`, `style`, `data-*` attributes"},"225":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-51","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/compo